{ White's main response, preparing to castle and putting the bishop on a more active square than in the 6. Be2 line. }
7... Qc7
{ In this variation, Black does not need to hurry with taking on  e5  since exf6 is not a threat: both Nxf6 and gxf6 are a bit better for Black. }
