12... Nf6 { This is as good as exd5 but keeps the tension in the center. } 13.
dxe6 Bc6 14. Qb3 c4 15. Qxc4 Rd4 16. f4 Qf5 17. Qb3 Rb4 18. Qd1 Bc5+ 19. Kh1
Re8 *

