Nxd4 9. Ng5 Nc6 10. Bf4 Nge7
{ Qxb2 may be even stronger, but it is also more difficult. The knight move leads to an advantage at little risk. }
11. Nc3 Ng6 12. Bxg6 hxg6
{ Black can continue with f6 and g5 or simply Be7 and Rc8. } *

