{ Allows Qxe5 after all, since after   12.Qf3  Ng6  White has difficulties with defending the e-pawn as well. }
12... Qxe5 13. Qf3 Bc6 14. Bf4 Qf6 15. Rad1 h5 { Threatens g5. } *

