{ The moves Ne7 and Nxf3 are also popular. It is not easy to decide which is best. I chose Bc5 because the idea behind it is straightforward. The bishop protects the knight on  d4  to prepare Bb5. Once the knight is protected by the bishop, the black queen is free to recapture on  b5  if necessary. }
