{ with an unclear position. But note that both captures on h7 fail. } 18. Nxh7
{ 18.Bxh7  Rxg5 } 18... Rxg2+ 19. Kxg2 Qg4+ 20. Kh1 Bxf2 21. Rxf2 d4+ *

